Installation:
Local Development Environment Setup:
Download and install XAMPP (or similar local server software).
Install Apache and MySQL services using XAMPP control panel.
Project Setup:
Clone the GitHub repository into the htdocs folder in the XAMPP installation directory (C:\xampp\htdocs\).
Rename the repository folder to uiu-studentsphere.
Database Setup:
Open phpMyAdmin through the XAMPP control panel.
Create a new database named uiu_studentsphere.
Import the provided SQL database file from the project's database folder.
Configuration:
Modify the config.php file in the includes folder to set up database connection parameters.
Running the Project:
Launch XAMPP and start Apache and MySQL services.
Open a web browser and navigate to http://localhost/uiu-studentsphere.
User Guide:
Registration and Login:
Register as a new user using the registration form.
Login using registered credentials.
Dashboard:
View and navigate through various features like events, galleries, forum posts, etc.
Creating Posts:
Click on respective sections to create event posts, forum posts, job postings, etc.
Fill in necessary details and submit.
Approval Process:
Admin will review and approve submitted posts.
Resource and Course Lectures:
Access resources and course lectures uploaded by administrators.
Edit and Delete:
Users can edit or delete their own posts.
Profile Management:
Edit user profile information and settings.
